creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Short Poetry Collection 136 by Various.
Read in English by J Korth; Son of the Exiles; DomBombadil; Shakira Searle; Ian King; Leonard Wilson; Bellona Times; filmmefatale; Winston Tharp; Bruce Kachuk; Algy Pug
This is a collection of 22 poems read by LibriVox volunteers for September 2014.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: librivox; audiobooks;poetry collection; short poetry
title: Short Poetry Collection 136
